PrecisAuthority to enter into the "ELK LAKE WATERLINE TRANSFER AGREEMENT" with the CORPORATION OF THE DISTRICT OF CENTRAL SAANICH and the CAPITAL REGIONAL DISTRICT which provides for the transfer to the Capital Regional District of the title to the lands associated with Elk Lake Reservoir, Stewart's Well and McTavish Reservoir, all of which are situated at various locations in North Saanich and Central Saanich, British Columbia.
